  m_Name: IntroDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  lines:
  - text: 'have sacrificed everything. My wife, my first child, my second child,
      my third child, my fourth child, '
  - text: my fifth child, my sixth child, my seventh child, my eighth child, my ninth
      child, my tenth child...
  - text: and then my parents, my siblings, my grandparents, my aunts, my uncles,
      my cousins, and every single one of my relatives.
  - text: But now, I think... I think it's time to pay the price. Dear Serenay, please
      help me.
